@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((v0 * (v1 + 0.90 * v2 + 0.77)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.93 * (v2 + 0.48 + v0 + 0.98)))
    v2 = (v2 / wp.sin(0.68))
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.06 - v0 + 0.34) * v2) + ((v1 + 0.34 + v0 + 0.11) - (v0 + 0.32 - v1 + 0.35)))
    v0 = 0.75
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.23) + tmp) + (v1 + wp.cos(tmp + 0.83)))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.cos(v0 + 0.31) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
